  <entry>
    <title>Anaconda python2.7ver SyntaxError: invalid syntax</title>
    <link href="http://argon1025.github.io/2020/05/26/Python/Python_Konlpy_2.7error/"/>
    <id>http://argon1025.github.io/2020/05/26/Python/Python_Konlpy_2.7error/</id>
    <published>2020-05-26T06:23:11.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-01-13T13:24:30.956Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Anaconda2 python2.7환경에서 특정패키지를 인스톨할때 SyntaxError: invalid syntax오류가 뜨면서 제대로 설치되지 않는 경우가 있다</p><p><a href="https://github.com/konlpy/konlpy">python konlpy</a>  설치도중 문제가 발생하여 이슈보고를 하였고 아래와같은 해결책을 찾을 수 있었다.<br></br></br></p><hr><p><a href="https://jpype.readthedocs.io/en/latest/install.html#binary-install">Jpype Doc</a>에 있는 내용</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">JPype can be installed as pre-compiled binary if you are using the Anaconda Python stack. Binaries are available for Linux, OSX, and windows on conda-forge.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Ensure you have installed Anaconda&#x2F;Miniconda. Instructions can be found here.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Install from the conda-forge software channel:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">conda install -c conda-forge jpype1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>한마디로 jpype를 conda-forge로 설치하고, 패키지를 설치하면 된다.</p><p></br></br></p><hr><p>이후 jpype를 conda-forge로 설치하고, 패키지를 설치하였다</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># conda install -c conda-forge jpype1</span><br><span class="line"># pip install konlpy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></br></br></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Anaconda2 python2.7환경에서 특정패키지를 인스톨할때 SyntaxError: invalid syntax오류가 뜨면서 제대로 설치되지 않는 경우가 있다&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/konlpy/konl</summary>
      
    
    
    
